== Births == * {{ill|Ken'en (Japan)|ja|建炎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1127|ja|1127|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 27|ja|11月27日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Xiaozong (Song)|ja|孝宗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the second emperor of the Southern Song († {{ill|1194|ja|1194|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Shōwa (Japan)|ja|承和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 9th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|842|ja|842|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 27|ja|11月27日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Prince {{ill|Abo|ja|阿保親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , first son of Emperor {{ill|Heizei|ja|平城天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and father of {{ill|Narihira|ja|在原業平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|792|ja|792|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kōji (Japan)|ja|Kōji|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1557|ja|1557|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|September 27|ja|9月27日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Go-Nara|ja|後奈良天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 105th emperor (* {{ill|1496|ja|1496|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1834|ja|1834|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 21|ja|11月21日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Sakai Tadayoshi (Isesaki Domain)|ja|酒井忠良 (伊勢崎藩主)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the lord of the Isesaki Domain (* {{ill|1808|ja|1808|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
