== Events == * {{ill|Enryaku|ja|延暦|qq=}} 13rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|794|ja|794|qq=}} {{ill|November 18|ja|11月18日|qq=}} ） – The capital was relocated during the Heian period; Emperor {{ill|Kanmu|ja|桓武天皇|qq=}} left Nagaoka-kyō for the new capital in Yamashiro (Heian-kyō). == Births == * {{ill|Ken'en (Japan)|ja|建炎|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1127|ja|1127|qq=}} {{ill|November 27|ja|11月27日|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Xiaozong (Song)|ja|孝宗|qq=}} , the second emperor of the Southern Song († {{ill|1194|ja|1194|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Shōwa (Japan)|ja|承和|qq=}} 9th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|842|ja|842|qq=}} {{ill|November 27|ja|11月27日|qq=}} ） – Prince {{ill|Abo|ja|阿保親王|qq=}} , first son of Emperor {{ill|Heizei|ja|平城天皇|qq=}} and father of {{ill|Narihira|ja|在原業平|qq=}} (* {{ill|792|ja|792|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kōji (Japan)|ja|Kōji|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1557|ja|1557|qq=}} {{ill|September 27|ja|9月27日|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Go-Nara|ja|後奈良天皇|qq=}} , the 105th emperor (* {{ill|1496|ja|1496|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1834|ja|1834|qq=}} {{ill|November 21|ja|11月21日|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Sakai Tadayoshi (Isesaki Domain)|ja|酒井忠良 (伊勢崎藩主)|qq=}} , the lord of the Isesaki Domain (* {{ill|1808|ja|1808|qq=}} ).
