'''October 22''' is the 22nd day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October (Lunisolar)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannazuki|qq=}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senshō|qq=}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Enryaku|ja|延暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enryaku|qq=}} 13rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|794|ja|794|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/794|qq=}}  {{ill|November 18|ja|11月18日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 18|qq=}} ） – The capital was relocated during the Heian period; Emperor {{ill|Kanmu|ja|桓武天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanmu|qq=}}  left Nagaoka-kyō for the new capital in Yamashiro (Heian-kyō).
== Births ==
* {{ill|Ken'en (Japan)|ja|建炎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ken'en (Japan)|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1127|ja|1127|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1127|qq=}}  {{ill|November 27|ja|11月27日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 27|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Xiaozong (Song)|ja|孝宗|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xiaozong (Song)|qq=}} , the second emperor of the Southern Song († {{ill|1194|ja|1194|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1194|qq=}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Shōwa (Japan)|ja|承和|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōwa (Japan)|qq=}} 9th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|842|ja|842|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/842|qq=}}  {{ill|November 27|ja|11月27日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 27|qq=}} ） – Prince {{ill|Abo|ja|阿保親王|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Abo|qq=}} , first son of Emperor {{ill|Heizei|ja|平城天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heizei|qq=}}  and father of {{ill|Narihira|ja|在原業平|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Narihira|qq=}}  (* {{ill|792|ja|792|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/792|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Kōji (Japan)|1=Kōji (Muromachi period)|2=ja|3=弘治 (日本)|lt=Kōji|4=ru|5=Кодзи (Муромати)|ja|Kōji|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōji (Japan)|1=Kōji (Muromachi period)|2=ja|3=弘治 (日本)|lt=Kōji|4=ru|5=Кодзи (Муромати)|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1557|ja|1557|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1557|qq=}}  {{ill|September 27|ja|9月27日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September 27|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Go-Nara|ja|後奈良天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Go-Nara|qq=}} , the 105th emperor (* {{ill|1496|ja|1496|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1496|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1834|ja|1834|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1834|qq=}}  {{ill|November 21|ja|11月21日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 21|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Sakai Tadayoshi (Isesaki Domain)|ja|酒井忠良 (伊勢崎藩主)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakai Tadayoshi (Isesaki Domain)|qq=}} , the lord of the Isesaki Domain (* {{ill|1808|ja|1808|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1808|qq=}} ).

