{{Not to be confused with|October 22|qq=October 22}}[[Category:Days of the Japanese Lunisolar Calendar]]<!--why is this category always showing up as 347 members?--> {{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十月廿二|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 10월 22일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar October|qq=}} '''October 22''' is the 22nd day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October (Lunisolar)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannazuki|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senshō|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 六曜}} .
== Events == * [[:en:Enryaku|Enryaku]] 13rd year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|794|ja|794|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/794|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 700}} [[:en:November 18|November 18]] ） – The capital was relocated during the Heian period; Emperor [[:en:Emperor Kanmu|Kanmu]] left Nagaoka-kyō for the new capital in Yamashiro (Heian-kyō). == Births == * {{ill|Ken'en (Japan)|ja|建炎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ken'en (Japan)|qq=}} 1st year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1127|1127]] [[:en:November 27|November 27]] ） – Emperor {{ill|Xiaozong (Song)|ja|孝宗|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xiaozong (Song)|qq=}} , the second emperor of the Southern Song († [[:en:1194|1194]] ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Jōwa|Shōwa (Japan)]] 9th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|842|ja|842|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/842|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 27|November 27]] ） – Prince [[:en:Prince Abo|Abo]] , first son of Emperor [[:en:Emperor Heizei|Heizei]] and father of [[:en:Ariwara no Narihira|Narihira]] (* {{ill|792|ja|792|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/792|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 700}} ). * [[:en:Kōji (Muromachi period)|Kōji]] 3rd year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|1557|ja|1557|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1557|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:September 27|September 27]] ） – Emperor [[:en:Emperor Go-Nara|Go-Nara]] , the 105th emperor (* {{ill|1496|ja|1496|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1496|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} ). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 5th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1834|ja|1834|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1834|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 21|November 21]] ） – {{ill|Sakai Tadayoshi (Isesaki Domain)|ja|酒井忠良 (伊勢崎藩主)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakai Tadayoshi (Isesaki Domain)|qq=}} , the lord of the Isesaki Domain (* {{ill|1808|ja|1808|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1808|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} ).
