== Deaths == * [[:en:Jōwa|Shōwa (Japan)]] 9th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|842|ja|842|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/842|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 27|November 27]] ） – Prince [[:en:Prince Abo|Abo]] , first son of Emperor [[:en:Emperor Heizei|Heizei]] and father of [[:en:Ariwara no Narihira|Narihira]] (* {{ill|792|ja|792|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/792|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 700}} ). * [[:en:Kōji (Muromachi period)|Kōji]] 3rd year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1557|1557]] [[:en:September 27|September 27]] ） – Emperor [[:en:Emperor Go-Nara|Go-Nara]] , the 105th emperor (* [[:en:1496|1496]] ). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 5th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1834|ja|1834|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1834|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 21|November 21]] ） – {{ill|Sakai Tadayoshi (Isesaki Domain)|ja|酒井忠良 (伊勢崎藩主)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakai Tadayoshi (Isesaki Domain)|qq=}} , the lord of the Isesaki Domain (* [[:en:1808|1808]] ).
